rows.label: qst201823_msg0003
rows.name: Mimi-san! You made it this far!

rows.label: qst201823_msg0005
rows.name:
I never thought the day
would come when I could
return to my own home...

rows.label: qst201823_msg0006
rows.name:
I'm so happy! It's all thanks
to you, Pepe, and everyone.

rows.label: qst201823_msg0007
rows.name:
No, no... We didn't
do anything special.

rows.label: qst201823_msg0008
rows.name:
Come on, let's not talk here.
Let's go to the settlement!

rows.label: qst201823_msg0009
rows.name:
I'm sure they'll celebrate!
For Mimi's return and for the
brave Uka and her friends!
